00:41:19,950 --> 00:41:21,420
<font size="64">- Yes. - We pulled together,</font>

1676
00:41:21,420 --> 00:41:22,620
<font size="64">- but I... - That's what we agreed to do.</font>

1677
00:41:22,620 --> 00:41:24,150
<font size="64">- wasn't even using half my power. - I see.</font>

1678
00:41:24,150 --> 00:41:25,590
<font size="64">- Were you scared? - Anyway,</font>

1679
00:41:25,690 --> 00:41:27,760
<font size="64">- since Ye Eun couldn't do it... - Right.</font>

