1683
00:41:30,190 --> 00:41:33,130
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(They're comforting her, which is unusual.)</font>

1684
00:41:30,430 --> 00:41:31,630
<font size="64">- It's the same as doing it. - That was beyond her control.</font>

1685
00:41:31,630 --> 00:41:33,060
<font size="64">- Exactly. - Right. What else could she do?</font>

1686
00:41:33,060 --> 00:41:34,630
<font size="64">- How could she have done it? - Exactly.</font>

1687
00:41:33,130 --> 00:41:35,300
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Thanks.)</font>

1688
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:35,630
<font size="64">- She just couldn't. - Right.</font>

1689
00:41:35,630 --> 00:41:38,030
<font size="64">She can do a penalty on the ground instead.</font>

1690
