00:42:43,100 --> 00:42:44,100
<font size="64">Seriously?</font>

1733
00:42:43,130 --> 00:42:46,200
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The goalpost welcomes them again.)</font>

1734
00:42:44,100 --> 00:42:45,940
<font size="64">Why are we doing another penalty shootout?</font>

1735
