00:42:46,870 --> 00:42:50,770
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(What kind of training is it?)</font>

1737
00:42:48,900 --> 00:42:50,010
<font size="64">Will Ju Yong be playing again?</font>

1738
00:42:50,010 --> 00:42:52,540
<font size="64">Here's the second mission for the Running Man Team.</font>

